bis-chart

Small shiny app to reproduce a chart from a BIS publication

The original chart

It can be found here : graph 1, on the left.

Data source

According to the chart description the data should be available here but the link does not work.

After some research, the CSV data could be found here.

This CSV file is not completely consistent. For instance, to reproduce the same figures as the original chart, sometimes the Maturity has to be set to :
- "Total (all maturities)",
and sometimes to
- "Over 1 year and up to 5 years" + "Up to and including 1 year" + "Over 5 years".

Since there are only 3 maturities, using one or the other should produce the same figures, but it does not.
